verbose_text: Surface expression of ICAM-1, MHC Class I, and MHC Class II was unaffected by exposure to either rTNF-alpha (1000 U/ml) or rIL-6 (100 U/ml) for 24 h. Under normal culture conditions, intracellular interleukin-6 (IL-6) and tumor necrosis factor-alpha (TNF-alpha) were detected immunohistochemically.
